Specific extraction rules for CoAs:
- "Not more than X ppm" → converted_ppm = X, evidence_type = "nmt"
- "X PPM MAX" → converted_ppm = X, evidence_type = "nmt"
- "≤ X ppm" → converted_ppm = X, evidence_type = "nmt"
- Result labeled "PASS" → confirmed batch testing done per USP <469> 
  → Tier 1 (present = Yes)
- Result labeled "FAIL" → material rejected, still present but out of spec

